Presented by the NYU Wagner Urban Planning Student Association      February 21, 2014   5:00pm - 6:00pm   Skyscraper Museum   39 Battery Pl, New York, NY 10280         Join UPSA on Friday, February 21st at 5pm for a tour of the Skyscraper Museum in Battery Park City (39 Battery Pl, New York, NY 10280) for a guided tour by the Founder, Director, and Curator Carol Willis!      Meet at the museum ten minutes before 5:00pm when the tour will begin. The tour will last approximately 45 minutes when the group will join a happy hour downtown with the American Planning Association!      UPSA will cover admission for the first 20 registrants, so RSVP soon!
